<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Rescheduled Registration Appointment</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .header {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .content {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .content p {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .content ul {
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-style: italic;
        }
        .highlight {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <p class="header">Dear [Customer's Name],</p>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>We regret that your registration appointment was cancelled. Below are the new details for your registration appointment:</p>

            <h3>Unit Details:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><span class="highlight">Unit Number:</span> [Unit Number]</li>
                <li><span class="highlight">Unit Size:</span> [Unit Size]</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Rescheduled Details:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><span class="highlight">Date:</span> [New Registration Date]</li>
                <li><span class="highlight">Time:</span> [New Registration Time]</li>
            </ul>

            <p>Please ensure you arrive at the venue at the scheduled time. If you have any questions or need further assistance, feel free to reach out to us.</p>

            <p>We look forward to completing your registration smoothly.</p>
        </div>

        <p class="footer">Warm regards, <br> Epitome Projects LLP</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>